Tell them, Dean!

20:12.200 --> 20:13.900
Tell them who you are!

20:14.000 --> 20:16.500
Nora, baby, don't listen
to anything they tell you!

20:16.700 --> 20:18.600
Okay, I can explain everything!

20:22.800 --> 20:24.700
WILLOWS:
Nothing you say
will change the DNA, Leo.

20:24.700 --> 20:26.100
That's your hair in that box.

20:26.100 --> 20:27.800
I already explained that.

20:28.000 --> 20:30.000
The problem is, we
still don't believe you.

20:30.000 --> 20:31.300
Look, I told you.

20:31.500 --> 20:32.500
I opened the box for Nora,

20:32.500 --> 20:35.400
I assembled the vacuum cleaner,
and I threw it out back.

20:35.400 --> 20:37.100
My hairs must have gotten
stuck in it then.

20:37.100 --> 20:38.100
End of story.

20:38.300 --> 20:39.700
Why the alias, Leo?

20:40.100 --> 20:41.200
Who're you hiding from?

20:42.500 --> 20:45.300
All right, okay,
one night, ten years ago,

20:45.300 --> 20:46.900
I did a hit of Ecstasy,

20:47.200 --> 20:49.500
