of peyote for good measure.

20:49.900 --> 20:52.100
By the time morning rolled
around, I was so high

20:52.100 --> 20:55.000
I thought I was inside
a living cartoon.

20:55.700 --> 20:58.700
I went outside naked
and performed a joyous,

20:58.700 --> 20:59.900
impromptu dance

20:59.900 --> 21:02.400
to the Egyptian Sun God Ra.

21:02.400 --> 21:03.800
That sounds really beautiful.

21:03.800 --> 21:05.600
I'm sorry I missed it.

21:05.600 --> 21:08.500
Well, unfortunately,
20 preschoolers

21:08.500 --> 21:10.400
playing in the yard
next door didn't.

21:11.100 --> 21:11.600
I was convicted

21:11.600 --> 21:15.200
of lewd and lascivious behavior,
public nudity.

21:15.200 --> 21:18.000
They forced me to sign up
on Megan's List.

21:19.200 --> 21:21.000
And my life went
right down the crapper.

21:21.800 --> 21:24.200
I've been hounded out of every
neighborhood I've moved into.

21:24.400 --> 21:26.000
Got my tires slashed.

21:26.400 --> 21:27.300
Someone...

21:28.600 --> 21:30.600
someone nailed
my cat to my door.

21:31.400 --> 21:33.100
I wouldn't worry about your cat.

21:33.400 --> 21:35.300
You've got bigger problems
right now.

21:38.400 --> 21:39.400
Who is she?

21:47.100 --> 21:49.100
She the one they found
the other night?

21:49.300 --> 21:52.000
Found dead in your box, Leo.

21:52.900 --> 21:55.200
The one that your vacuum
cleaner came out of.

21:55.500 --> 21:57.700
The one that you got
your arm hairs stuck in.

21:58.900 --> 22:00.100
I didn't have anything to do

22:00.450 --> 22:01.300
with that little girl.

22:04.450 --> 22:06.350
I never saw her
before in my life.

22:06.400 --> 22:08.500
You're living
in an unregistered apartment,

22:08.650 --> 22:11.950
under an assumed name,
in violation of your parole...

22:12.000 --> 22:13.800
No! That's not true!
I still have my own place...

22:14.100 --> 22:16.200
Which we're going to go through
with a fine-tooth comb.

22:16.450 --> 22:18.750
Your own fianc?doesn't
even know who you are.

22:19.250 --> 22:21.300
Please, please... You're not
going to tell her, are you?

22:21.700 --> 22:23.500
Let's say that ship's
already sailed.

22:26.500 --> 22:27.450
Put him in the tank.

22:28.250 --> 22:31.700
You've never...
done anything you've regretted?

22:32.050 --> 22:33.850
More than there are stars
in the sky.

22:34.800 --> 22:35.750
?????

22:36.000 --> 22:36.900
????

22:40.450 --> 22:41.850
????apartment,

22:41.900 --> 22:43.750
where he claims
he threw away the box;

22:43.800 --> 22:46.100
which, somehow ended up
three blocks north

22:46.350 --> 22:49.100
and two blocks east--
with Baby Cordelia dead in it.

22:49.450 --> 22:51.300
Do you really believe
he killed the girl

22:51.800 --> 22:55.000
and carried her five blocks
before dumping the body?

22:55.300 --> 22:58.100
In that neighborhood, who would
notice a guy carrying a box?

22:58.150 --> 23:00.700
Leo Finley was never even
charged with child molestation,

23:00.750 --> 23:02.000
let alone abuse.

23:02.350 --> 23:03.900
Sex offenders escalate.

23:04.000 --> 23:05.700
He has a reasonable
explanation why his hairs

23:05.750 --> 23:06.900
were in the box,

23:07.450 --> 23:08.850
and there was no evidence
of the victim

23:09.100 --> 23:10.650
at either
of his residences.

23:10.700 --> 23:11.600
I know.

23:12.400 --> 23:13.750
So why is he still in custody?

23:13.800 --> 23:16.650
Because he lied to us before,
and he's still lying now.

23:17.900 --> 23:19.600
<i>Analysis of the oily residue</i>

23:19.650 --> 23:20.800
from the cardboard box.

23:22.300 --> 23:22.950
It's oil.

