Yeah, mostly 10-W-40,
transmission fluid,

23:25.750 --> 23:27.550
a little bit of axle grease
and some dirt mixed in.

23:27.900 --> 23:30.100
Well, that could be from any
parking lot or street in town.

23:30.350 --> 23:33.600
Yeah, but site-specific    impurity levels could
narrow that down a bit.

23:34.350 --> 23:36.400
Let me know if you find
any suspicious oil slicks.

24:05.600 --> 24:06.400
Excuse me.

24:07.150 --> 24:08.050
Sir?

24:09.200 --> 24:10.000
How you doing?

24:10.800 --> 24:12.000
My name's Nick Stokes.

24:12.050 --> 24:13.600
I'm with the Las Vegas
Crime Lab.

24:13.650 --> 24:15.000
