Come here, kids.
Come on.

33:20.100 --> 33:22.450
Let's get everyone else
out you got in there.

33:23.900 --> 33:25.200
They didn't do
anything, Boyd.

33:26.000 --> 33:27.000
You got
to let them out, too.

33:30.300 --> 33:31.400
Work with me
here, Boyd.

33:33.400 --> 33:35.600
We're gonna
work it out.

33:37.200 --> 33:38.150
All right, let's go.

33:39.100 --> 33:40.050
Come on, you guys go first.

33:40.350 --> 33:41.700
Let's go. Let's go.

33:41.850 --> 33:43.050
Come on, come on, come on!

33:43.400 --> 33:44.000
I'm letting you go.
Come on...

33:44.050 --> 33:44.850
They're coming out!

33:45.500 --> 33:46.300
Nice and easy.

33:50.000 --> 33:51.200
Go, go. Move,
move, move, move!

33:51.250 --> 33:52.050
All right, let's see this

33:52.100 --> 33:53.250
through to the end.

33:53.900 --> 33:55.700
Now, you've got a choice.

33:56.400 --> 33:57.900
You both can
come out together,

33:58.500 --> 34:00.200
or you can send your
wife ahead of you.

34:01.800 --> 34:02.600
Come on, you got to go.

34:02.650 --> 34:03.450
No! No!

34:03.500 --> 34:05.400
Come on. Listen to me.

34:05.650 --> 34:07.050
Don't argue.
You got to go.

34:08.300 --> 34:10.550
You're going.
No.

34:10.800 --> 34:11.850
Go, go, go.
I don't want

34:11.900 --> 34:12.750
to go without you!
Just go!

34:12.800 --> 34:13.650
Don't argue
with me.

34:15.350 --> 34:17.199
Hold you fire! Hold your fire!

34:17.250 --> 34:19.199
Hold your fire!
Hold your fire!

34:29.750 --> 34:32.949
??? then you locked her
under the sink.

34:33.449 --> 34:36.050
If you say I killed Inez,
that must have been how it was.

34:36.150 --> 34:38.350
You know, however you want
it put, that's fine with me.

34:39.000 --> 34:39.900
Oh.

34:40.300 --> 34:43.600
I-I'm just... I'm just trying
to do you justice here, Boyd.

34:44.199 --> 34:45.199
Just write it out,

34:45.750 --> 34:46.850
and I'll sign it.

34:47.050 --> 34:48.900
So, you're waiving your right
to counsel?

34:48.949 --> 34:50.600
I don't need no lawyer.

34:50.900 --> 34:51.699
It's over.

34:51.750 --> 34:53.150
Can we just get this thing done?

34:53.600 --> 34:55.100
All right.

34:57.800 --> 34:59.600
I want   my daddy!
Okay, come on.

34:59.700 --> 35:00.800
Just leave him alone!
Come with me now!

35:00.900 --> 35:03.300
I want my daddy!
He wants his daddy!

35:03.350 --> 35:04.200
It'll be okay.
Excuse me?

35:05.050 --> 35:06.400
Could you give me a minute
with them, please?

35:06.450 --> 35:07.250
Thank you.

35:10.650 --> 35:11.650
It's going
to be okay.

35:12.100 --> 35:14.300
But you got
to be brave.

35:15.050 --> 35:16.100
Can you do that?

35:17.200 --> 35:18.850
Is this because of us?

35:19.150 --> 35:20.600
No, no.

35:20.650 --> 35:21.600
No, it's not because of you.

35:21.650 --> 35:24.100
Is it because
of what happened to Inez?

35:24.750 --> 35:26.000
What do you think
happened to her?

35:27.100 --> 35:28.500
We were playing a game.

35:29.950 --> 35:30.650
A game?

35:30.700 --> 35:31.550
Hide and seek.

35:32.950 --> 35:33.950
Hide and seek?

35:34.400 --> 35:36.050
Dad was asleep on the couch.

35:39.550 --> 35:41.300
You said that you were playing
hide and seek?

35:41.950 --> 35:42.750
He was it.

35:43.150 --> 35:44.850
He found me right away, but...

35:45.550 --> 35:46.800
but Inez won.

35:50.000 --> 35:53.450
I showed her the best hiding
place in the whole house.

35:54.450 --> 35:57.050
Four, five, six,

35:57.100 --> 35:59.300
seven, eight,

35:59.400 --> 36:01.950
nine, ten, 11.

36:02.400 --> 36:04.600
12, 13...

36:14.450 --> 36:17.000
Did your dad tell you
to say this?

36:17.250 --> 36:20.400
No. You're not supposed
to wake Dad when he's sleeping

36:20.450 --> 36:22.400
because he gets tired a lot.

36:36.150 --> 36:37.600
Why don't you tell me
what really happened?

36:40.000 --> 36:41.400
You got my confession.

36:42.500 --> 36:44.150
Yes, but I don't believe
that's what happened anymore.

36:46.200 --> 36:47.750
I told you, that's how it was.

36:50.600 --> 36:52.150
Your kids are telling me
something different.

36:54.750 --> 36:56.200
It was an accident,
wasn't it, Boyd?

36:57.350 --> 36:58.150
All right,
think about this.

36:58.200 --> 36:59.450
Think about
your children.

