Oh.

40:42.900 --> 40:43.700
What are you doing here?

40:44.050 --> 40:45.350
I was waiting for you.

40:47.900 --> 40:48.700
How did you get in here?

40:48.900 --> 40:50.500
Can't we talk about
something interesting?

40:51.200 --> 40:52.300
Me, for instance.

40:53.100 --> 40:53.900
I'm interesting.

40:54.800 --> 40:55.900
