40:56.000 --> 40:56.800
Let's talk about you.

40:57.300 --> 40:59.000
For starters, Nora left me.

41:00.100 --> 41:02.350
Actually, she threw my
stuff out in the street,

41:02.550 --> 41:04.750
got a restraining
order on me, notified

41:04.800 --> 41:05.950
the neighbors
and called my boss.

41:06.800 --> 41:09.300
"Hey, scumbag,
don't bother coming in.

41:09.600 --> 41:11.050
We'll mail you your last check."

41:11.800 --> 41:14.150
So, in one fell swoop,
as it were,

41:14.300 --> 41:16.500
I lost my girlfriend,
my livelihood

41:17.500 --> 41:18.550
and my place to live.

41:20.400 --> 41:21.950
I thought it was going to
be different this time.

41:24.450 --> 41:25.800
Frankly, I blame you.

41:27.250 --> 41:28.650
I didn't create
the circumstances

41:28.700 --> 41:29.550
of your life, Leo.

41:29.550 --> 41:31.850
You grind up the innocent
with the guilty.

41:31.900 --> 41:33.300
Just take it easy.

41:33.350 --> 41:34.650
I was just doing my job.

41:34.700 --> 41:36.750
I was just   doing my job?
Yeah, I was just

41:36.800 --> 41:38.300
doing my job.
I was just  doing my job.

41:38.350 --> 41:39.700
I was just
following orders.

41:39.750 --> 41:41.200
Blond Nazi bitch!

41:43.200 --> 41:44.100
You get in there

41:44.100 --> 41:46.550
with your big boots,
and you kick it all apart,

41:46.850 --> 41:48.500
and you don't care who you hurt,

41:49.200 --> 41:51.600
whose life you destroy
in the process.

41:51.800 --> 41:52.950
Calm down.
No.

41:53.000 --> 41:55.200
It's not fair!
Just calm down!

41:55.250 --> 41:56.500
Calm down...
