Would that help you to forget

42:03.400 --> 42:04.800
how completely
you screwed my life up?

42:05.450 --> 42:06.800
Would you sleep
better at night?

42:08.150 --> 42:09.900
Maybe I should just
save you the trouble

42:09.950 --> 42:11.100
