42:11.550 --> 42:12.450
What do you think?

42:14.100 --> 42:15.600
I think you need
to talk to somebody.

42:16.600 --> 42:18.000
I am talking to somebody.

42:19.600 --> 42:20.400
I'm talking to you.

42:23.050 --> 42:24.250
So how about this?

42:24.500 --> 42:26.100
If I do decide to kill myself,

42:26.150 --> 42:27.400
I'm going to come over
to your house

42:28.300 --> 42:30.300
